org.eclipse.viatra.integration.mwe2

Interface IPublishTo

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PublishTo

    public interface IPublishTo
    Provides an interface for handling message publishing to a topic. The objects implementing the IPublishTo interface define a topic name, and an IMessageFactory object that is repsonsible for creating the messages sent to the specified topic.
